Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.67,0:00:09.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,《失落的祕符》前情提要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Previously on "The Lost Symbol"...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.67,0:00:11.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,這是一個重大突破\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is breakthrough stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.41,0:00:13.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,而且我們也許只發現了冰山一角\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And we may only be scratching the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.11,0:00:15.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,扎克里·所羅門死於土耳其的監獄暴動\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Zachary Solomon died in a prison riot in Turkey.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.09,0:00:15.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fs10\frz357.5\b0\3a&HFF\c&H7C6E7E\pos(261.6,43.2)}機密信息
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.55,0:00:17.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,-我們需要蘭登  -那彼得·所羅門呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- We need Langdon. - What about Peter Solomon?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.75,0:00:20.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,彼得在天堂和地獄之間的分界線\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Peter is in the borderland between Heaven and Hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.21,0:00:21.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,他可能已經死了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He might already be dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.46,0:00:23.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,-這只是塊石頭  -這是一幅地圖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- It's a piece of rock. - It's a map!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.69,0:00:27.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,金字塔和尖頂石會揭示出入口的位置\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The pyramid and the capstone will reveal the location of the portal.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.04,0:00:28.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,希伯來文...是密碼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Hebrew... it's code.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.67,0:00:31.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,那枚戒指可能包含某種解密祕鑰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The ring could contain some kind of decryption.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.28,0:00:32.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,我在照你的意思做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am doing what you wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.75,0:00:34.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,我叫你單獨行動\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You were told to do it alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.36,0:00:35.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,甩掉她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Cut her loose.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.62,0:00:43.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,你不能待在這裏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, you can't be in here, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.10,0:00:44.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,公園關門了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Park's closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.02,0:00:46.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,身份證拿出來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's see some ID.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.99,0:01:06.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,醫生說他的搭檔應該能痊癒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The doctors say his partner should make a full recovery.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.03,0:01:10.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,那他呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.11,0:01:12.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,現在下定論爲時尚早\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Too early to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.68,0:01:18.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,我曾被派往七千英里之外去打極端主義者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I got sent 7,000 miles away to fight extremists.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.55,0:01:22.64,*Default,,0,0,0,,這不是你的戰爭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This isn't your fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.98,0:01:27.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,我身上的彈孔可不是這麼說的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I got a hole in my side that says otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.50,0:01:30.81,*Default,,0,0,0,,昨天有件證物失蹤了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Some evidence went missing yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.85,0:01:32.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,彼得·所羅門的戒指\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Peter Solomon's ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.30,0:01:34.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,你不會恰好知情吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You happen to know anything about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.65,0:01:36.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,你在說什麼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.34,0:01:37.81,*Default,,0,0,0,,我是說  如果...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm saying if--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.09,0:01:39.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,假設...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}hypothetically--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.19,0:01:42.64,*Default,,0,0,0,,你在幫蘭登和凱瑟琳\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you were aiding Langdon and Katherine,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.97,0:01:45.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,那你這麼做只會將他們置於險境\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you'd only be putting them in more danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.43,0:01:48.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,你無法從做了這些事的人手中保護他們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can't protect them from the guy who did this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.73,0:01:52.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,你沒必要擔心我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You don't have to worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.39,0:01:55.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,我已經逞夠英雄了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm done playing the hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.47,0:01:59.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,我向我妻子承諾過\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Made my wife a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.25,0:02:02.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,你最好能遵守諾言\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Make sure you keep it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.33,0:02:17.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,甜蜜的家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Home sweet home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.51,0:02:20.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,你做了炸香蕉嗎  親愛的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, you make tostones, babe?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.59,0:02:22.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,別抱太大希望\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wouldn't get my hopes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.93,0:02:24.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,什麼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.03,0:02:26.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎回家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.22,0:02:29.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,-你好呀  -感覺如何\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Hey. - How you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.95,0:02:32.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,餓死了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.60,0:02:35.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,我是說過你們可以待在這裏破譯聖經密碼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I said you guys could set up here, to crack your Bible code,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.16,0:02:37.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,沒說把我的食物都吃光\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}not eat all my food.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.52,0:02:40.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,我就不打擾你和你的新朋友們了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll leave you to your new friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.24,0:02:45.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,-也許我們該走了  -別啊  她沒事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Maybe we should go. - No. She's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.39,0:02:48.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,她只是擔心我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's just worried about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.17,0:02:50.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,再說了  我覺得現在別出去比較好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Besides, I wouldn't go anywhere right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.44,0:02:51.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,我們有個尾巴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We got a lurker.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.39,0:02:54.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,隔壁第三棟  北面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Three houses down, north side.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.07,0:03:02.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,-他找到我們了  -不  那是佐藤的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- He's found us. - No, it's Sato's people.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.14,0:03:03.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,她去醫院找過你們倆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She came to the hospital looking for you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.99,0:03:05.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果你猜錯了  那是邁拉克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And if you're wrong and it's Mal'akh
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.87,0:03:07.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,或是他派來的人  那怎麼辦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}or someone he sent, what then?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.72,0:03:10.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,他爲何要那樣做  他需要你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why would he do that? He needs you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.41,0:03:13.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麼了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's going on with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.43,0:03:15.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,沒有  沒事  我沒事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nothing. Nothing, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.04,0:03:16.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,別糊弄我  羅伯特\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't bullshit me, Robert.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.99,0:03:23.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,有些事我沒告訴你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's something I haven't told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.73,0:03:28.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,我們在圖書館時  他打來了電話\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He called when we were at the library.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.51,0:03:29.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,誰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.28,0:03:31.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,邁拉克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mal'akh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.26,0:03:36.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,他說得很清楚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And he made it very clear
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.35,0:03:39.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,他想讓我單獨行動\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that he wants me doing this on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.54,0:03:42.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,不能帶你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.60,0:03:46.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,-你之前沒告訴我  -我不想嚇到你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- And you didn't tell me this before? - I didn't want to scare you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.85,0:03:49.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎  還是你也贊同他的想法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Right. Or maybe you agree with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.53,0:03:52.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,也許你覺得單獨行動會更好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe you think you'd be better off doing this alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.77,0:03:54.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,-這不是贊同與否的問題  -我爸在他手上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- It's not about agreeing with him. - He has my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.12,0:03:55.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,而是承認他所呈現的一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's about acknowledging the very
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.15,0:03:56.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,-非常危險  -我哪裏也不去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- real danger he presents. - I'm not going anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.73,0:03:57.82,*Default,,0,0,0,,他有真正的殺手...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He has a literal assassin...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.83,0:04:00.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,你覺得這就能讓我停手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And that's what it's going to take to get me to stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.35,0:04:34.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,貝拉米先生  埃裏森·布萊克  中情局\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. Bellamy, Ellison Blake, Central Intelligence.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.49,0:04:36.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉讓你久等了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.25,0:04:37.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,我可不信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, I doubt that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.66,0:04:42.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,看來你一點沒浪費時間\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Looks like you put your time here to good use.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.60,0:04:44.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,抓緊時間看書\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Caught up on a little reading.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.45,0:04:46.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,我懷念書\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Uh, I miss books.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.23,0:04:50.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,科幻小說  曾是我的初戀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sci-fi-- that was my first love.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.98,0:04:51.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,我知道這不是高雅讀物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know it's not high art,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.99,0:04:53.68,*Default,,0,0,0,,但這股吸引\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but the stakes--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.68,0:04:57.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,還有什麼比世界末日的故事更刺激精彩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I mean, how can you beat a story about the end of the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.88,0:05:01.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,現在我沒什麼時間看書了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't get much time to read anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.67,0:05:03.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,不看小說了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not fiction.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.35,0:05:06.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,不過沒關係  因爲我發現\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But that's okay, because I've come to realize
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.21,0:05:08.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,最有趣的故事...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that the most interesting stories...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.60,0:05:11.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,是真實存在的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...are true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.60,0:05:16.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道這是什麼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know what that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.25,0:05:17.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.20,0:05:21.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,這是利維坦社的符號\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's the sign for the Leviathan Group.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.67,0:05:25.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,這是共濟會的一個祕密組織\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's a secret sect within the Freemasons,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.64,0:05:27.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,你所屬的組織\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to which you belong.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.19,0:05:31.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,我還知道  他們的目的是爲了保護\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I also know that their purpose is to protect
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.05,0:05:34.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,一些非常古老  非常有價值的信息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}some very old, very valuable information.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.06,0:05:38.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,所以我想問你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So my question for you is:
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.33,0:05:40.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,它在哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}where is it?
