Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.59,0:17:19.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,篡改《聖經》文本的人替換了一些詞\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Whoever altered the Bible text replaced some of the words.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.55,0:17:20.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,在《列王紀上》中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In First Kings,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.73,0:17:24.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,上帝將聰明智慧賜予所羅門\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}God gave Solomon a wise and understanding heart,
