Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.57,0:17:30.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,但是這裏的文本被人篡改了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But here that script was changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.61,0:17:33.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,不再是"聰明智慧"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It no longer reads "Wise and understanding heart."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.51,0:17:35.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,而只是"睿智"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It just reads "Wisdom."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.87,0:17:38.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,這對於幫你破譯信息有用嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So that's supposed to help you unscramble the letters?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.51,0:17:40.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,這就是所謂的關鍵詞密鑰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's what's known as a keyword cipher.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.41,0:17:41.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,就像這樣  你們看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It works like this. Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.51,0:17:44.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,你把"睿智"兩個詞的字母從字母表中取出\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You pull the letters of "Wisdom" out of the alphabet
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.07,0:17:45.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,將其放在前面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and place them at the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.54,0:17:47.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,希伯來語的音譯放在這邊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Hebrew transliteration goes here,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.58,0:17:49.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,然後翻譯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and then you translate.
