Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.18,0:20:46.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,否則我會有更多信息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Otherwise I'd have more information than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.07,0:20:48.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,所以你要進去那裏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's why you're gonna go in there
