Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.25,0:21:01.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,所以放下後悔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So put aside regrets...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.51,0:21:04.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,做你最擅長乾的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and do what you do best.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.67,0:21:15.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,我真不敢相信  這太扯了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't believe this. It's bullshit.
