Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.19,0:22:17.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,只要這樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do that,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.51,0:22:20.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,就沒有人  包括你父親\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and no one... including your father,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.24,0:22:23.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,需要知道這件事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}needs to know anything about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.09,0:22:30.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,我很喜歡這地方  已經到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's kind of gotten to the point
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.14,0:22:32.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不能在別的地方工作的地步\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}where I-I can't work anywhere else.
