Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.02,0:27:03.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,你要拿它做什麼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What are you gonna do with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.60,0:27:06.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,我會按下那個按鈕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm gonna push that button.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.56,0:27:08.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,然後你把我想知道的都告訴我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then you're gonna tell me what I want to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.86,0:27:12.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,你的上司不喜歡弄髒他的手嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your boss doesn't like getting his hands dirty?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.61,0:27:14.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,所以他把這事交給了你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So he leaves that to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.03,0:27:17.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,本質上  是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Essentially, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.99,0:27:20.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,但他和我並不總是意見一致\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But he and I don't always see eye to eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.17,0:27:37.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,這是A80短程電磁脈衝發射器\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is an A80 short-range EMP generator.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.43,0:27:39.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,我剛剛讓攝像頭短路了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just shorted out the cameras.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.22,0:27:40.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,很快他們就會帶來新的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Pretty soon they'll bring new ones,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.60,0:27:43.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,但在那發生之前的一切完全是我們之間的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but whatever happens before then is completely between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.43,0:27:48.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不在乎能不能找到入口\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look, I don't care about finding some portal.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.98,0:27:51.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,我只是想找到你的朋友彼得·所羅門\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just want to find your friend Peter Solomon.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.82,0:27:57.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,中情局一般不會參與失蹤人口的調查\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}CIA doesn't generally involve itself in missing persons.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.45,0:27:59.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,我有自己的原因\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have a personal interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.75,0:28:08.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,他兒子扎克里曾是我們的線人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}His son Zachary was one of our assets.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.71,0:28:11.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,我知道是因爲我招募了他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know because I recruited him.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.30,0:28:16.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,這是我第一次和這麼年輕的人一起工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was the first time I'd worked with someone so young.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.09,0:28:19.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,還英年早逝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.35,0:28:22.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,我以爲他能應付得來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I thought he could handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.06,0:28:30.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,當他因爲販毒被關進監獄時\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When he was thrown into prison for trafficking,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.77,0:28:33.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,我接到命令  要否認與他有任何瓜葛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was ordered to disavow any knowledge of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.27,0:28:35.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,放棄他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To burn him.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.82,0:28:40.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,所以我照做了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So that's what I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.33,0:28:44.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,那又怎樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.29,0:28:48.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,你覺得找到彼得就會讓一切都好起來嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You think finding Peter will make everything all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.42,0:28:52.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,不會\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.92,0:28:56.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,但這將是一個開始\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But it'd be a start.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.72,0:29:01.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,我們快沒時間了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're running out of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.14,0:29:06.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,我對抓走他的人一無所知\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look, I don't know anything about the man who took him.
