Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.14,0:29:10.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果我知道那是什麼  我就能理解他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If I understand that, I can understand him,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.35,0:29:14.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,這可能決定了彼得的生或死\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and that might be the difference between Peter living and dying.
