Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.96,0:29:40.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,-你要幹什麼  -別擔心  我能搞定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What are you doing? - Don't worry, I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.68,0:29:44.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,窄的地方另說  但我不怕高\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tight spaces are one thing; heights I can handle.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.18,0:29:45.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,爲什麼會有人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why would somebody hide
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.97,0:29:47.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,把尖頂石藏在骨灰缸裏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}a capstone in an urn anyway?
