Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.61,0:30:01.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,救了我們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Saved us.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.90,0:30:04.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,而你想讓我覺得你不迷信嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And you want me to believe you're not superstitious?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.91,0:30:06.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,我只是在擔心干擾因素\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was worried about the noise.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.37,0:30:08.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,好吧...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.95,0:30:11.82,*Default,,0,0,0,,證明一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}prove it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.09,0:30:23.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,我們有麻煩了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We got a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.88,0:30:25.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,這裏面除了骨灰  什麼都沒有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's nothing in here but ash.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.68,0:30:27.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,什麼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.52,0:30:33.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,這還不僅是我們唯一的麻煩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's not our only problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.65,0:30:36.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,有人知道我們在這裏了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Someone knows we're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.90,0:30:38.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,-誰  -不重要  我們得走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Who? - Doesn't matter. We have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.98,0:30:40.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果有人想要阻止我們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If someone's trying to stop us,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.08,0:30:41.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,意味着我們找對了地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that means we're on the right track.
