Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.64,0:31:17.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  我有件事要坦白\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I have a confession to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.02,0:31:22.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,我坐下時  就知道你的身份\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I knew exactly who you were when I sat down.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.11,0:31:28.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不明白\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't understand.
