Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.80,0:31:44.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,你現在該離開了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You should probably go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.47,0:32:34.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,慢點\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Easy.
