Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.24,0:32:52.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,好的  埋葬  沒被埋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, um, buried, not buried.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.87,0:32:56.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,14個字母  智慧  列王  心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}14 letters. Wisdom. Kings. Heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.91,0:32:59.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,他馬上到了  而你還把我們鎖住了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's almost here, and you locked us in!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.58,0:33:00.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  是啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.17,0:33:02.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah.
