Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.29,0:33:46.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,等等  等等\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wait. Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.76,0:33:51.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,在這裏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.26,0:33:57.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,-這不是尖頂石  -趕緊拿上走人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- It's not the capstone. - Just take it and keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.82,0:34:09.64,*Default,,0,0,0,,這裏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.99,0:34:15.82,*Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.37,0:34:25.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,約拿是如何逃脫的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How did Jonah get out again?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.38,0:34:28.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,上帝發令了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}God commanded it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.46,0:34:31.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,現在就是好時機\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, now would be a good time.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.79,0:35:11.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,蘭斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, hey, Lace.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.09,0:35:12.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,最近如何  兄弟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's up, man?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.88,0:35:14.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,是的  我知道  抱歉  現在很晚了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, I know. I'm sorry. It's late.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.72,0:35:17.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  沒事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, yeah, no, all good.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.05,0:35:18.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,我今天出院了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, I got out today.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.55,0:35:19.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,聽着\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, listen, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.10,0:35:24.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,你們發現了關於槍手的任何信息嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you, uh, you got anything on the shooter?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.23,0:35:28.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,我知道  中情局說是什麼"絕密"信息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, yeah, I know, the CIA got some "Eyes only" Bullshit,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.23,0:35:31.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,但我們的監控拍到了他  對嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but... we got him on camera, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.78,0:35:34.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,在克里爾維尤系統裏搜一下  給我個名字\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So run him through Clearview, get me a name.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.78,0:35:37.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  明天可以\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, tomorrow works fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.32,0:35:39.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,謝了  我欠你個人情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thanks, man. I owe you one.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.45,0:35:41.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right, man,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.99,0:35:44.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,你繼續看保齡球什麼的吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}go back to watching bowling or whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.46,0:35:46.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.93,0:35:59.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,附近的所有單位\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...all units in vicinity,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.47,0:36:01.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,代碼1號  亞當斯紀念醫院\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Code 1, Adams Memorial.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.60,0:36:04.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,無反應女性  身份未知\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nonresponsive female, yet to be identified.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.77,0:36:07.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,現場發現黑紅色廂式旅行車\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Black and red SUV found at scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.44,0:36:09.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,馬里蘭州牌照\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maryland license plate number...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.24,0:36:16.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,彼得\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Peter...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.15,0:36:19.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,把我召進了利維坦社\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}brought me into the Leviathan Group.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.62,0:36:23.82,*Default,,0,0,0,,是他揭示了它的目的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He was the one who revealed its purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.99,0:36:29.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,所有共濟會都會講述關於深藏祕密的故事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All Masons tell stories about deeply held secrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.58,0:36:33.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,大多數是爲了激起新成員興趣的怪談\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Most of them are tall tales to intrigue new members.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.59,0:36:35.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,但這個不一樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But this was different.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.15,0:36:41.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fs18\frz2\b0\3a&HFF\c&H11112D\move(402,64.533,188,76.8)}史密森尼博物館所有
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.84,0:36:41.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,我在這些人身上看到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I saw in these men
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.85,0:36:43.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,一種信仰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}a belief...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.85,0:36:48.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,信仰超越可能的事物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}in something beyond possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.81,0:36:51.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,信仰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A belief
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.48,0:36:54.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,古老的智慧不僅真實存在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that the ancient wisdom was not only real,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.32,0:36:57.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,而且還能解除意識\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but that it could unlock consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.69,0:36:59.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,讓人能進入\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}allowing man to access
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.78,0:37:02.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,隱藏的權力寶庫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}hidden reservoirs of power.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.66,0:37:06.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,這個組織建立在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The group was formed
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.29,0:37:09.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,兩個問題的基礎上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}based on two questions:
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.21,0:37:13.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,人類能否應對這樣的演變\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Could humanity handle such an evolution?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.38,0:37:15.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果這個權力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And what might happen
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.55,0:37:19.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,落入壞人手中會發生什麼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}if this power fell into the wrong hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.60,0:37:27.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,我們協定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We made a pact
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.14,0:37:30.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,要保衛那些線索\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to safeguard the clues.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.56,0:37:37.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,但是神話的誘惑力很強\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But the lure of the myth was strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.37,0:37:48.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,傳言\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's a story
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.00,0:37:51.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,上個世紀初\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}of a member of the group
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.87,0:37:54.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,該組織有一個成員\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}from the beginning of the last century
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.63,0:37:57.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,對他來說  誘惑太大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}for whom the lure was too great.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.26,0:38:03.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,他拋棄了他的誓言\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He abandoned his oath.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.64,0:38:05.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,他爲自己尋求智慧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He sought the wisdom for himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.68,0:38:09.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,他也找到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And he found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.31,0:38:14.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,據說他學會了控制事物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It is said that he learned to control things,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.31,0:38:18.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,他可以使物質屈服於他的意志\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that he could bend matter to his will.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.39,0:38:49.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,天吶\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, God.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.92,0:39:27.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,我09年在法蘭克福用過脈衝發射器這招\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I did an EMP gambit in Frankfurt in '09.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.51,0:39:30.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,當時可沒有這些\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I didn't have one of these.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.47,0:39:32.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,我就用車庫搖控器\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'd use a garage door opener.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.19,0:39:37.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,你想怎麼處置他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do you want to do with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.15,0:39:40.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,放了他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Cut him loose.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.61,0:39:43.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,現在你獲得了他的信任  可以根據需要利用他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now that you've bonded, you can use him as needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.92,0:40:04.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,是他嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is it him?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.01,0:40:11.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an9\bord1\fs18\b1}指幾部存在於希臘文七十士譯本\N但不存在於希伯來文聖經的著作
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.01,0:40:11.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,是一句出自《次經》的引述\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's a quote from the Apocrypha.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.26,0:40:15.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,《馬加比家族》的第四本書\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fourth Book of the Maccabees.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.94,0:40:21.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,"你若因你的不順服\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"For if you dispose me to anger
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.15,0:40:22.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,而使我發怒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"By your disobedience...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.78,0:40:28.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,你將迫使我用可怕的刑罰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"You will compel me, with dreadful punishments...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.45,0:40:32.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,來毀滅\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"...to destroy
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.74,0:40:36.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,你們所有人"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}every one of you."